article.headline: Ohio secures 84-68 win against Robert Morris
article.description: — AJ Clayton scored 16 points as Ohio beat Robert Morris 84-68 on Saturday.
article.linkText: Ohio secures 84-68 win against Robert Morris
article.story: ATHENS, Ohio -- — AJ Clayton scored 16 points as Ohio beat Robert Morris 84-68 on Saturday. Clayton had seven rebounds for the Bobcats (3-5). Victor Searls scored 14 points and added seven rebounds. Jackson Paveletzke and Aidan Hadaway both scored 11 points. The Colonials (6-3) were led by Josh Omojafo, who recorded 15 points. Antallah Sandlin'El added 14 points for Robert Morris. Alvaro Folgueiras finished with 12 points and seven rebounds. The loss ended a six-game winning streak for the Colonials. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
